<item>
            <title>[LU-14632] sanity-hsm test_606: losetup: /dev/mapper/mds1_flakey: failed to set up loop dev</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14632</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;To reproduce:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;setup Lustre with config mds1_HOST !=&#160;mds1failover_HOST;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;without llmount.sh before the test run:&#160;&#160;ONLY=606 sh sanity-hsm.sh&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test fails with :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;

&#160; &#160; &#160; losetup: /dev/mapper/mds1_flakey: failed to set up loop device:&#160;No such file or directory

&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The reason of failure:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;After check_and_setup_lustre() mds1_dev is equal to&#160;/dev/mapper/mds1_flakey, which is unexported to saved real&#160;device&#160; (/dev/vdc) by stop():&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;

&#160; &#160; &#160; stop mds1

&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; elif dm_flakey_supported mds1; then

&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; dm_cleanup_dev mds1

&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; unexport_dm_dev mds1

&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As a result test_606():stack_trap() is called with non existing&#160;&#160;/dev/mapper/mds1_flakey:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;

stack_trap &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;stop mds1; start mds1 /dev/mapper/mds1_flakey&#160;-o rw,user_xattr&apos;&lt;/span&gt; EXIT

&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;and failed as:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;

&#160;losetup: /dev/mapper/mds1_flakey: failed to set up loop device:&#160;No such file or directory

&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
